      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor\"\u003eEditor\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona\"\u003ePersona\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eInheritance Hierarchy\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUObject\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUPersonaPreviewSceneController\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eReferences\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona\"\u003ePersona\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eHeader\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e/Engine/Source/Editor/Persona/Public/PersonaPreviewSceneController.h\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInclude\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e#include \"PersonaPreviewSceneController.h\"\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSyntax\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003eUCLASS \u0026#40;Abstract\u0026#41;  \nclass UPersonaPreviewSceneController : public UObject  \n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRemarks\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBase class for preview scene controller (controls what the preview scene in persona does)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eFunctions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d0681dcd-808f-4a72-b5e9-90659993cabf/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/775ec001-52ba-4dab-ad2f-1864971829a2/api_function_virtual.png\" alt=\"Virtual\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Virtual\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/PropertyEditor/IDetailPropertyRow\"\u003eIDetailPropertyRow\u003c/a\u003e *\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/UPersonaPreviewSceneController/AddPreviewContro-\"\u003eAddPreviewControllerPropertyToDetails\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c class \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/IPersonaToolkit\"\u003eIPersonaToolkit\u003c/a\u003e \u003e\u0026 PersonaToolkit,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/PropertyEditor/IDetailLayoutBuilder\"\u003eIDetailLayoutBuilder\u003c/a\u003e\u0026 DetailBuilder,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/PropertyEditor/IDetailCategoryBuilder\"\u003eIDetailCategoryBuilder\u003c/a\u003e\u0026 Category,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FProperty* Property,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/PropertyEditor/EPropertyLocation__Type\"\u003eEPropertyLocation::Type\u003c/a\u003e PropertyLocation\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCalled when populating the preview scene settings details panel to allow customization of the controllers properties.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5915e6ec-2363-4e16-ab84-dda7ecdb7052/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/26525366-9528-41f6-8397-f9bac70c363c/api_function_virtual.png\" alt=\"Virtual\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Virtual\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4081dbbd-0fdc-4901-b361-449963ba1e61/api_function_const.png\" alt=\"Const\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Const\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/UPersonaPreviewSceneController/InitializeView\"\u003eInitializeView\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nUPersonaPreviewSceneDescription* SceneDescription,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/IPersonaPreviewScene\"\u003eIPersonaPreviewScene\u003c/a\u003e* PreviewScene\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCalled when this preview controller is activated.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/54351cef-7b37-4b1a-8633-686480dd9497/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/de18c7e5-857c-44fa-886f-2e5faaea588c/api_function_virtual.png\" alt=\"Virtual\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Virtual\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8845fc5a-8020-4766-8ba6-3fbc1b594119/api_function_const.png\" alt=\"Const\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Const\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/UPersonaPreviewSceneController/UninitializeView\"\u003eUninitializeView\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nUPersonaPreviewSceneDescription* SceneDescription,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Editor/Persona/IPersonaPreviewScene\"\u003eIPersonaPreviewScene\u003c/a\u003e* PreviewScene\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCalled when this preview controller is deactivated.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
